ŁChristopher Richardson Parris
1979 - 2010
"His smile lights the sky at night, his freckles are the stars
he wraps his soul around us all, and it's then we hear his laugh""░
ŁIn Loving Memory of
Terence James Donovan
15 August 1942 - 15 December 2015
Remembering you is easy, we do it everyday.
Missing you is a heartache, that never goes away."▒
«"I wish I had the healing words
to wrap around the quiet,
Wish I knew some magic ways,
to lighten up your night,"
by Andrew W.S. Kenny: beautiful father, fantastic friend"▓
»KENNETH NELSON
1930         (ACTOR)          1993    
(TEXAS)                          (LONDON)
       Life was FANTASTIC      
                                      NAOMI"┐
